<div class="w3-panel w3-yellow">
  <pre><code>{{ JSON user }}</code></pre>
</div>

<div class="w3-panel w3-blue">
  <pre><code>{{ JSON users }}</code></pre>
</div>

{{else}}
<div class="w3-panel w3-red">
  <h3>You are not logged in.</h3>
  <p>Consectetur accusantium debitis perspiciatis cum vitae quasi dolore placeat Odio atque ipsum porro neque dolor? Similique libero eligendi quia dolore necessitatibus? Ea asperiores atque id repellendus architecto. Minima doloribus eos?</p>
